snippet.title: NBA 2K21: Official PS5 Teaser Trailer (In-Engine)
snippet.description: Check out this first look at NBA 2K21 running in-engine on PlayStation 5. NBA 2K21 is built from the ground up to fully utilize the incredible power, speed, and technology of PS5.
